{"tid":1216943,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[小心]呢個聯署怪怪地","createTime":"2019-06-13T11:28:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T11:33:13.000Z","uid":40679,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b01ac928fcb126812e9f57926b9c5670da8bbff7","tid":1216943,"uid":40679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:28:49.000Z","msg":"有個台灣朋友問我有冇簽呢個聯署<br />\n我關注呢件事咁耐都未見過有人話簽呢個網站<br />\n就㩒入去睇下<br />\n一開始俾名都冇問題<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fXZdDNG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfXZdDNG.png&h=9bad7f29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後要怪怪地<br />\n要我地share先可以繼續<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Za5DPUn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZa5DPUn.png&h=a0d1b59a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我搵到個skip for now嘅option之後繼續<br />\n最後居然要我地幫手簽其他野先可以完成個簽署<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/06/13/190154_5a608f667ce70907c7abad9c462baf2d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F06%2F13%2F190154_5a608f667ce70907c7abad9c462baf2d.png&h=2e336420&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家要小心 唔好個個網站都信<br />\n驚過多資料顯示俾人睇會中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a47c7d27b326578e7f63d06c659940b3782125c","tid":1216943,"uid":40679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:29:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c472370387043610f35f18dd6119edf8051367d","tid":1216943,"uid":40679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:29:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffa9fc5c87af4508e2a463251d9d4799a200fd1f","tid":1216943,"uid":40679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:29:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a77f3fe8566263ae4919938ffac56f65f16b17da","tid":1216943,"uid":4783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"cite